    <summary>Free Universal Database Tool</summary>
    <description>
        <p>**NOTE: This is a community package of DBeaver Community and not officially
          supported by DBeaver Corporation.**</p>
      <p>This repackaging is not supported by DBeaver Corporation.</p>
        <p>Free multi-platform database tool for developers, SQL programmers, database
            administrators and analysts. Supports all popular databases: MySQL, PostgreSQL, MariaDB,
            SQLite, Oracle, DB2, SQL Server, Sybase, MS Access, Teradata, Firebird, Derby, etc.</p>
    </description>
